OL,7,FFormer England captain and 2003 World
OL,8,FCup winner Lewis Moody has been
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with motor neurone disease.
OL,11,FMoody, who used to play for Bath
OL,12,FRugby, announced his diagnosis on
OL,13,FInstagram on the morning of Monday 6
OL,14,FOctober.
OL,16,FThe 47-year-old said the diagnosis has
OL,17,Fbeen "incredibly hard to process" and
OL,18,Fcame as a "huge shock" to both him and
OL,19,Fhis family.
