OL,7,FHe said: "I'm writing to share some
OL,8,Ftough news. I have recently been
OL,9,Fdiagnosed with ALS, also known as
OL,10,FMotor Neurone Disease (MND).
OL,12,F"This has been incredibly hard to
OL,13,Fprocess and a huge shock to me and my
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,F"I feel fit and well in myself and I'm
OL,17,Ffocused on staying positive, living
OL,18,Flife and dealing with the changes /
OL,19,Fwill experience as they come.
