OL,4,CMoody diagnosed with motor neurone
OL,5,Cdisease
OL,7,F"I am being well supported by my
OL,8,Ffamily, friends and medical
OL,9,Fprofessionals and I'm truly grateful
OL,10,Fto those who, in their time, helped
OL,11,Fprogress research to support others,
OL,12,Flike me, living with this disease.
OL,14,F"Since retiring from the sport I love,
OL,15,Fand alongside my wife Annie, l've been
OL,16,Fable to dedicate much of the past 12
OL,17,Fyears to fundraising for The Lewis
OL,18,FMoody Foundation in support of those
OL,19,Faffected by brain tumours."
